Building Binary Distributions
=============================

Distributions are generated using stdeb. To build the Debian package python-hackclock, execute:

    python setup.py --command-packages=stdeb.command bdist_deb

To debug installation:

    sudo dpkg -D113 -i deb_dist/python-hackclock_2.0-beta-1_all.deb

To uninstall:

    sudo dpkg -r python-hackclock

Running Locally
===============

To test locally:

    export PYTHONPATH=/Users/deckerego/Projects/hack-clock/lib
    ./scripts/run_server.py --config /Users/deckerego/Projects/hack-clock/tests/localsettings.conf
